I mean, it's a cool feature of course, but how can I guess that   categoriesSelected = getArguments().getPa.... would not give me a new pointer ? Dammit, I lost two hours of my life ! I bet I am not the first to make this mistake. Happily it wasn't that hard to debug but I couldnot figure out where the problems could be. Halalala, what a shame on me. But, it's a funny things. A two hours bugs solved just by one ligne of code ! (the stuff is MainActivity is just some refactoring because sometimes I don't know how to spell english variables).
